  "texts": [
    "The framework seamlessly integrates modern technologies, including IoT, 5G, mobile edge computing, and BCT, addressing critical challenges in data security, consensus processing, key management, and privacy standards within smart healthcare applications.",
    "Below, a detailed overview of all six layers is provided.",
    "Sensing layerThe first layer of the SSEHCET is the sensing layer, which consists of wearable or implantable IoT sensors attached to the human body.",
    "These IoT sensors collect Fig. 5 Proposed Framework SSEHCET patients' vital signs, which are collected by the smart device connected to these sensors [60][61][62].",
    "This smart device application monitors the vitals and transmits them to the next layer in case the vitals are not normal."
  ]
}